* CHECK TIMESTAMPS!

* Check copyright dates, update if necessary.

* Update NEWS and RELEASES files.

* Change version in configure.ac, run "./bootstrap".

* Build and test the programs!

* Make sure all files are checked into RCS/CVS.

* Run "rcs2log -h ties.org -i 1" and edit the ChangeLog.

* Check the new ChangeLog into RCS/CVS.

* Run "./configure; make distcheck; make distclean".

* Create patch from previous release with "diff -urN".

* Build new RPMs.  (Maybe sign here instead of below?)

* Sign tarball, patch and RPM packages.

* Place online on FTP server.

* Upgrade gangplank demo server.

* Announce release on Freshmeat and gangplank homepage.
